      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical and in-house FDA FEA code are validated commercial/government tools with documented QA procedures; version-controlled scripts reviewed by independent analyst.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA solvers (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under formal software QA plans. Version control, change logs, and independent code review are documented. Achieved level meets required level for Medium model risk."
